data.description: Charming wood house with brick facade on quiet street. Driveway with covered parking + bonus garage / shed in backyard, which can be accessed through wooden gate. This house is Smart, with both lock system and thermostat. Updated kitchen and baths, with touchless faucet in the kitchen. Rear yard access. Large primary bedroom. High grade laminate flooring installed in 2016. Carpet only in 2 bedrooms. Large bonus room in back (counted toward sq. ft. in listing). Flood Zone X (C).
